text: Tyler Harding (born 18 October 1996) is a British freestyle skier. He competed in the 2013 and 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:British male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Great Britain Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
